      1          /** @addtogroup SRICTachometerLLI
      2           *  @{
      3           *  @file       SRICTachometerLLI.c
      4           *
      5           *  @brief      SR Input Capture based Tachometer reading
      6           *
      7           *  @details    This module implements the SR methods for reading a tachometer input which provides to the microcontroller
      8           *              a square wave signal whose frequency range is expected to be between 0 to 1KHz.
      9           *
     10           *              The 0 Hz detection, which is critical for the system, is made through a configurable timeout timer.
     11           *
     12           *  @defgroup   CLASS_B
     13           *
     14           *  @copyright  Copyright 2017-2018. Whirlpool Corporation. All rights reserved - CONFIDENTIAL
     15           *  }@
     16           */
